BRAINROT DUNGEON — CODEX BUILD SPEC
1. Core Loop
Player enters dungeon
 → kill Brainrot
   → gain Exp + Gold (+ chance Bone)
     → upgrade gear / pet / stats
       → fight Elite
         → fight Boss
           → rebirth to scale progression

Auto Farm chỉ là hành động thay thế attack của player.

2. Auto Farm System
Goal: Player tự tìm và đánh quái gần nhất
Behavior:
When AutoFarm = ON:
    find nearest enemy within detection range
    move toward enemy
    attack using normal attack cooldown

Restrictions:
    chỉ dùng basic attack
    không dùng skill
    vẫn nhận drop như bình thường

3. Enemy Types
3.1 Brainrot (Normal)
Config:
    Damage
    RangeAttack
    HP
    Cooldown (default = 1s)
    AttackType = SingleTarget
Drop:
    Exp
    Gold
    Low chance Bone
3.2 Elite Brainrot
Spawn random
Drop:
    Exp
    Gold
    Bone
    HP Item
3.3 Boss Brainrot
Abilities: AOE damage skill
Reward rule:
    LastHitPlayer → 50% Bone + buff item
    Remaining Bone → distributed by damage contribution
    All → Exp + Gold

4. Player Progression
Level
Gain Exp → Level Up
Each level → +10 stat points
Level requirement unlock higher weapons

Stats allocation

Player can distribute points into own attributes (no limit specified).

5. Equipment System
Upgrade Star
3 same equipment → chance upgrade star
Star range: 1 → 5
Each star → increase % attributes

Rarity
Tier	Random Stats Count
Normal	1
Unnormal	2
Rare	3
Epic	4
Legendary	4 + Lucky

Possible random attributes:
    +Exp
    +Damage
    +Gold
    +Armor
    +HP
    +Lifesteal%
    +HP Regen

6. Pet System
Player can summon mini Brainrot after defeating them.
Pet effects:
    Increase player damage
    Increase player HP
    Pet level up using Bone

7. Rebirth System
Reset level to lower value
Reset exp bar to 0%

For each rebirth:
    -10 level
    -10 stats each type
    +10% Gold gain permanently
    +10% Exp gain permanently

Infinite rebirth allowed

8. Currency System
Earn
    Action	Reward
    Kill Brainrot	Exp + Gold (+ chance Bone)
    Kill Elite	Exp + Gold + Bone 
    Kill Boss	Exp + Gold + Bone + HP, Lucky item, Items (unormal, race, epic)
    Spend

Gold:
    Upgrade equipment
    Buy HP items
    Upgrade skills


Bone:
    Buy equipment
    Upgrade pet, Skill
    Exchange to Gold

9. Skill System

    Player equips:
    1 Active
    1 Passive

    Active Skills
    Fixed damage
    Fixed heal
    Speed buff
    Stun / Freeze (2s)

    Passive Skills
    Heal over time (1–3%/s)
    Damage increase (10–20%)
    HP increase (20–40%)

    Upgrade cost: Bone

10. Shop & Monetization
Premium Vip: Boost in 7 day
    +25% Exp
    +25% Gold
    +25% Bone
    + Bone = level * rebirth  * 10 ( tùy theo gói, mua nhiều rẻ hơn)
    + +1 Legendary items

Paid items:
    Exp boost
    Gold boost
    Move speed boost
    HP potions
    Pet lifesteal ability
    Gacha legendary equipment

11. Ranking
Leaderboard categories:
    Level
    Diamond farm
    Power score
        Power score formula based on:
            Level
            Equipment
            Rebirth count
--------------------
Thêm phần 12 — GAME ENGINE RULES (QUAN TRỌNG NHẤT)

12. Server Authority Rules
Combat
All damage is calculated on SERVER only.
Client responsibilities:
    send attack intent
    play animation
    display effects
Server responsibilities:
    validate cooldown
    detect hit
    apply damage
    calculate drops
    distribute rewards
Client never decides:
    damage
    drop
    exp
    gold
    Movement

Player movement → client controlled
Monster movement → server controlled

Auto Farm:
    client sends "AutoAttackIntent"
    server controls target selection and attack execution
    Cooldown
    Cooldown is owned by server.
    Client may predict cooldown for UI
    but server is final authority.
    Rewards

Server calculates:
    exp
    gold
    bone
    item drop
    Server sends result to client
    Boss Damage Contribution
Server tracks:
    PlayerDamage[UserId] += damage
On boss death:
    LastHitPlayer gets 50% bone
    Remaining distributed proportionally
    Data Storage
Server owns player data:
    PlayerData:
    Level
    Exp
    Gold
    Bone
    Stats
    Equipment
    Rebirth
    Skills
    Pet
Client only receives a copy (readonly)
Anti Exploit Rule
If client sends attack faster than cooldown:
    ignore request
If client sends damage:
    ignore
If client sends drop:
    ignore

Build architecture MMORPG theo pattern chuẩn:

Client
    Input → RequestAction

Server
    Validate → Simulate → Result

Client
    Display Result


Tức là:

game tự động có architecture MMORPG chuẩn